name: automaton
css:
@-moz-document domain("automaton-media.com") {
.td-header-top-menu-full,
.td-header-menu-wrap-full,
.td_block_trending_now,
.td_block_big_grid_7,
.td-pb-span4,
.td-block-row,
.block-title,
.td-footer-template-14,
.td-sub-footer-container,
.td-crumb-container,
.author-box-wrap,
.td-related-title,
.td_block_related_posts,
.catlists,
.ai-viewport-1,
.social4i,
ul.ajaRecommend,
.ajarecommend-credit,
.td-header-style-10 .td-banner-bg,
[class*="td-g-rec-id-custom_ad"]
{display:none !important;}

.page-nav
{margin:0;}

.td-main-page-wrap
{padding-top:0;}

.td_module_10
{padding-bottom:20px;}

.td-header-style-10 .td-logo-wrap-full,
.td-header-wrap,
.td-header-sp-logo,
.td-logo,
.td-main-logo,
.td-header-style-10 .td-header-sp-logo img
{min-height:40px; line-height:40px; height:40px;}

.td-header-style-10 .td-logo-wrap-full a
{display:block;}

.td-header-sp-logo img
{margin-top:-10px;}

.td-pb-row
{margin:0 auto; float:none;}

.td-pb-span8
{width:100%;}

.post header .entry-title
{font-size:35px;}

.td-post-featured-image img
{margin:0 auto 26px auto;}

.td-post-template-default .td-post-featured-image img
{width:100%;}

}
